'''安東尼·約翰·布林肯'''（{{lang-en|Antony John Blinken}}，{{bd|1962年|4月16日}}），[[美国|美国]]外交事務專家及政府官員，现任[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]]（第71任）。[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]政府時期曾任[[美国总统行政办公室|美國國家安全副顧問]]及[[美國副國務卿|副國務卿]]。

在克林頓政府任職期間，布林肯曾在[[美国国务院|國務院]]和[[美國國家安全會議|國家安全會議]]擔任高級職務。在布殊政府時期，他為[[戰略與國際研究中心|戰略與國際研究中心]]的高級研究員，以及[[美国参议院|美国参议院]][[美國參議院外交委員會|外交委員會]]的[[幕僚長|幕僚長]]。奧巴馬時期，布林肯為總統過渡團隊的成員。其後於2009年至2013年間，布林肯擔任總統副助理和副總統的國家安全顧問。2017年後，布林肯開展私人企業工作，聯合創立了一家政治戰略諮詢公司。

== 早年生涯 ==
布林肯於1962年4月16日在[[紐約州|紐約州]][[揚克斯_(紐約州)|揚克斯]]出生，父母為[[猶太裔|猶太裔]]美國人，其父{{link-en|唐納德·M·布林肯|Donald M. Blinken}}（Donald Mayer Blinken,1925年11月11日-）曾在[[比爾·克林頓|比爾·克林頓]]執政時任{{Link-fr|美國駐匈牙利大使館|Ambassade des États-Unis en Hongrie|美國駐匈牙利大使}}。<ref name="twp">{{cite news|last1=Horowitz|first1=Jason|date=2013-09-20|title=Antony Blinken steps into the spotlight with Obama administration role|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/antony-blinken-steps-into-the-spotlight-with-obama-administration-role/2013/09/15/7484a5c0-1e20-11e3-94a2-6c66b668ea55_story.html|access-date=2013-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130916033942/http://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/antony-blinken-steps-into-the-spotlight-with-obama-administration-role/2013/09/15/7484a5c0-1e20-11e3-94a2-6c66b668ea55_story.html|archive-date=2013-09-16|id={{ProQuest|1432540846}}|page=C1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JVL">{{cite web|title=Antony 'Tony' Blinken|url=https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/biography/blinken.html|publisher=猶太虛擬圖書館|date=2013|access-date=2015-11-16|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117024905/https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/biography/blinken.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Frehm – Blinken |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1957/12/07/archives/frehmblinken.html |website=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |access-date=2020-11-23 |date=07-12-1957 |archive-date=2017-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324015517/http://www.nytimes.com/1957/12/07/archives/frehmblinken.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的祖父母為匈牙利猶太人。<ref>{{Cite web|last1=Andriotakis|first1=Pamela|date=August 25, 1980|title=Sam and Judith Pisar Meld the Disparate Worlds of Cage and Kissinger in Their Marriage|url=https://people.com/archive/sam-and-judith-pisar-meld-the-disparate-worlds-of-cage-and-kissinger-in-their-marriage-vol-14-no-8/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123113007/https://people.com/archive/sam-and-judith-pisar-meld-the-disparate-worlds-of-cage-and-kissinger-in-their-marriage-vol-14-no-8/|archive-date=2020-11-23|access-date=2020-11-25|website=[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]|dead-url=no}}</ref>而布林肯的叔叔{{link-en|艾倫·布林肯|Alan Blinken}}，則同在克林頓執政時期擔任{{Link-fr|美國駐比利時大使館|Ambassade des États-Unis en Belgique|美國駐比利時大使}}。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Russell|first=Betsy Z.|date=2020-11-23|title=Why Biden's pick for Secretary of State has a name that's familiar in Idaho politics...|language=en|work=Idaho Press|url=https://www.idahopress.com/eyeonboise/why-bidens-pick-for-secretary-of-state-has-a-name-thats-familiar-in-idaho-politics/article_33e80624-4a4f-51fb-807a-0f01157befdf.html|access-date=02-12-2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129201944/https://www.idahopress.com/eyeonboise/why-bidens-pick-for-secretary-of-state-has-a-name-thats-familiar-in-idaho-politics/article_33e80624-4a4f-51fb-807a-0f01157befdf.html|archive-date=2020-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Finnegan|first=Conor|date=2020-11-24|title=Who is Tony Blinken? Biden taps close confidante, longtime aide for secretary of state|language=en|work=ABC News|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/tony-blinken-biden-taps-close-confidante-longtime-aide/story?id=74363232|access-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202013112/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/tony-blinken-biden-taps-close-confidante-longtime-aide/story?id=74363232|archive-date=2020-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

其後，布林肯於紐約就讀[[道爾頓學校|道爾頓學校]]，至1971年為止。<ref name="JVL" />同年，其母親Judith Frehm Pisar（1937年2月17日-）與父親離婚，他與媽媽及媽媽的再婚丈夫，猶裔律師{{link-en|塞繆爾·皮薩爾|Samuel Pisar}}遷到[[巴黎|巴黎]]（Samuel Pisar,1929年3月18日-2015年7月27日）生活，皮薩爾為[[納粹大屠殺|納粹大屠殺]]的倖存者。<ref name="twp" />在巴黎生活時，他於{{link-en|珍妮曼努埃爾學校|École Jeannine Manuel}}就讀。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Bezioua|first=Céline|title=Venue d'Antony Blinken à l'école|url=https://www.ecolejeanninemanuel.org/fr/news-tous/item/77-venue-d-antony-blinken-a-l-ecole.html|access-date=2020-08-08|publisher=珍妮曼努埃爾學校|language=fr-fr|archive-date=2018-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420043225/http://www.ecolejeanninemanuel.org/fr/news-tous/item/77-venue-d-antony-blinken-a-l-ecole.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布林肯於1980年至1984年間在[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]就讀，<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|last=Rodríguez|first=Jesús|date=2021-01-11|title=The World According to Tony Blinken—in the 1980s|url=https://www.politico.com/news/magazine/2021/01/11/tony-blinken-secretary-state-harvard-crimson-college-writing-new-republic-columns-world-view-456699|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112062107/https://www.politico.com/news/magazine/2021/01/11/tony-blinken-secretary-state-harvard-crimson-college-writing-new-republic-columns-world-view-456699|archive-date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-12|website=[[Politico|Politico]]|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>主修社會研究，並為校內每周出版的美術雜誌《[[哈佛克里姆森報|哈佛克里姆森報]]》的共同編輯。<ref name="twp"/><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|last1=Uribe|first1=Raquel Coronell|last2=Griffin|first2=Kelsey J.|title=President-elect Joe Biden Nominates Harvard Affiliates to Top Executive Positions|url=https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2020/12/7/biden-cabinet-harvard-affiliates/|date=2020-12-07|access-date=2020-12-07|work=哈佛克里姆森報|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112031532/https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2020/12/7/biden-cabinet-harvard-affiliates/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thecrimson.com/writer/6331/Anthony_J._Blinken/ |title=Anthony J. Blinken |work=The Harvard Crimson |access-date=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2016-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210203436/http://www.thecrimson.com/writer/6331/Anthony_J._Blinken/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>布林肯在任編輯期間，曾在該報刊登多篇評論時政的文章。<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Paumgarten|first1=Nick|title=A Dad-Rocker in the State Department|date=2020-12-07|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2020/12/14/a-dad-rocker-in-the-state-department|access-date=09-12-2020|work=[[紐約客|紐約客]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112031610/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2020/12/14/a-dad-rocker-in-the-state-department|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4" />布林肯從哈佛大學畢業，獲得學士學位後，在《[[新共和|新共和]]》周刊實習了大約一年。<ref name="JVL" /><ref name=":4" />1985年，他進入[[哥倫比亞法學院|哥倫比亞法學院]]，並於1988年獲得[[法律博士|法律博士學位]]，<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|date=2015-04-30|title=Deputy Secretary of State Antony Blinken '88 Speaks at Annual D.C. Alumni Dinner|url=https://www.law.columbia.edu/news/archive/deputy-secretary-state-antony-blinken-88-speaks-annual-dc-alumni-dinner|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918180356/https://www.law.columbia.edu/news/archive/deputy-secretary-state-antony-blinken-88-speaks-annual-dc-alumni-dinner|archive-date=2020-09-18|access-date=2020-11-23|publisher=[[哥倫比亞法學院|哥倫比亞法學院]]|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>畢業後於紐約及倫敦開展執業生涯。<ref name="nj">{{cite news|last1=Sorcher|first1=Sara|title=Antony Blinken, Deputy National Security Adviser|date=2013-07-17|url=http://www.nationaljournal.com/decision-makers/security/antony-blinken-deputy-national-security-adviser-20130717|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214174259/http://www.nationaljournal.com/decision-makers/security/antony-blinken-deputy-national-security-adviser-20130717|archive-date=2015-02-14|work={{link-en|國家期刊|National Journal}}|accessdate=2021-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>1988年，布林肯與爸爸攜手為[[1988年美國總統選舉|1988年美國總統選舉]]的民主黨提名人[[麥可·杜卡基斯|麥可·杜卡基斯]]籌集資金。<ref name=twp />

1987年，布林肯以學士畢業論文為基礎，<ref name=":3" />出版專著《同盟與同盟：美國，歐洲和西伯利亞管道危機》。書中，布林肯認為在{{link-en|西伯利亞管道危機|Urengoy–Pomary–Uzhhorod pipeline}}期間，美國對[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]施加外交壓力對美國利益而言意義不大，更應維持美國與[[歐洲|歐洲]]之間的牢固盟友的關係。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Miller|first=Chris|title=The Ghost of Blinken Past|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/12/03/blinken-secretary-state-alliances-nato-ally-versus-ally/|date=03-12-2020|access-date=05-12-2020|website=[[外交政策_(雜誌)|外交政策]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206153644/https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/12/03/blinken-secretary-state-alliances-nato-ally-versus-ally/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 政府及私人職務生涯 ==
=== 克林頓及布殊時期 ===
在二十年間，布林肯曾在克林頓及布殊政府中擔任高級外交政策職務。<ref name="twp" />1994年至2001年間，布林肯為[[美國國家安全會議|美國國家安全會議]]的成員。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|last1=Gaouette|first1=Nicole|last2=Hansler|first2=Jennifer|last3=Atwood|first3=Kylie|title=Biden picks loyal lieutenant to lead mission to restore US reputation on world stage|date=2020-11-24|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/23/politics/blinken-biden-secstate-candidate/index.html|access-date=2020-11-26|work=[[有線電視新聞網|CNN]]|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125205721/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/23/politics/blinken-biden-secstate-candidate/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1994年至1998年間，布林肯為總統特別助理兼戰略規劃高級總監，以及兼任國安會演講稿的高級寫作總監。<ref name="statedeptbio">{{Cite web|title=Antony J. Blinken|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/236057.htm|access-date=2020-11-26|publisher=[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123111318/https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/236057.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1999年至2001年間，任總統特別助理兼歐洲和加拿大事務高級總監。<ref name=Gallucci09>{{cite book |title=Instruments and Institutions of American Purpose |last1=Gallucci |first1=Robert |author-link=Robert Gallucci |year=2009 |publisher=Aspen Institute |location=美國 |isbn=9780898435016 |page=112 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=T0NgQCkNwUkC&lpg=PA112 |access-date=2015-01-20 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123052539/https://books.google.com/books?id=T0NgQCkNwUkC&lpg=PA112 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2003年，他支持美國[[伊拉克战争|進軍伊拉克]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Glueck|first1=Katie|last2=Kaplan|first2=Thomas|date=12-01-2020|title=Joe Biden's Vote for War|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/12/us/politics/joe-biden-iraq-war.html|access-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118064050/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/12/us/politics/joe-biden-iraq-war.html|archive-date=2020-11-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Fordham|first1=Evie|date=2020-11-23|title=Biden secretary of state pick Blinken criticized over Iraq War, consulting work|work=[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞]]|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/biden-secretary-of-state-blinken-iraq-war-criticism|access-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123173648/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/biden-secretary-of-state-blinken-iraq-war-criticism|archive-date=2020-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>2002年，布林肯被任命為[[美國參議院外交委員會|美國參議院外交委員會]]的幕僚長，任期至2008年為止。<ref name=":0" />布林肯在當時協助時任外交關係委員會參議員[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]制定方針，奠定了拜登對美國進軍伊拉克的支持，並將拜登投票支持進軍伊拉克定性為「對實現艱困民主的一票」。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Johnson|first=Jake|date=2020-11-27|title=As Biden taps Blinken as Secretary of State, critics denounce support for invasions of Iraq, Libya|url=https://www.salon.com/2020/11/27/as-biden-taps-blinken-as-secretary-of-state-critics-denounce-support-for-invasions-of-iraq-libya_partner/|access-date=05-12-2020|website={{link-en|髮廊 (網站)|Salon (website)|髮廊}}|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201093605/https://www.salon.com/2020/11/27/as-biden-taps-blinken-as-secretary-of-state-critics-denounce-support-for-invasions-of-iraq-libya_partner/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在美國入侵和佔領伊拉克的數年間，布林肯協助拜登在參議院中提出了一項提案，建議在伊拉克建立按種族或宗派劃分的三個獨立地區。然則，該提議在國內以及總統[[喬治·沃克·布希|喬治·沃克·布希]]的反對下遭到大比數反對。<ref name="defender">{{Cite news|last1=Jakes|first1=Lara|last2=Crowley|first2=Michael|last3=Sanger|first3=David E.|date=2020-11-23|title=Biden Chooses Antony Blinken, Defender of Global Alliances, as Secretary of State|language=en-US|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/22/us/politics/biden-antony-blinken-secretary-of-state.html|access-date=05-12-2020|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123015015/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/22/us/politics/biden-antony-blinken-secretary-of-state.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他亦是[[戰略與國際研究中心|戰略與國際研究中心]]的高級研究員。2008年，布林肯為拜登{{link-en|喬·拜登2008年總統競選活動|Joe Biden 2008 presidential campaign|總統競選活動}}的一員，協助拜登爭取民主黨總統提名。<ref name="twp" />在奧巴馬及拜登當選正副總統後，他是{{link-en|巴拉克·奧巴馬總統交接|Presidential transition of Barack Obama|奧巴馬及拜登正副總統交接}}團隊的一員。<ref name="LaMonica">{{cite news |title=Blinken confirmed by Senate as Kerry's deputy at State |last1=LaMonica |first1=Gabe |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/17/politics/blinken-senate-confirmation/ |publisher=CNN |date=2014-12-17 |access-date=03-02-2015 |archive-date=2015-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150220022426/http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/17/politics/blinken-senate-confirmation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

