l |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年6月，布林肯指出自2014年末美國領導的聯軍發起針對[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的空襲以來，空襲已殺死超過一萬名伊斯蘭國的戰士，<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mroue |first1=Bassem |title=U.S. official: Airstrikes killed 10,000 Islamic State fighters |url=https://eu.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/06/03/islamic-state-death-toll/28415743/ |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |date=03-06-2015 |access-date=05-12-2020 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206153624/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/06/03/islamic-state-death-toll/28415743/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>並指出伊斯蘭國將面臨站不住腳的情況。<ref>{{cite news |title=US: Coalition has killed 10,000 ISIL fighters |url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/6/3/us-coalition-has-killed-10000-isil-fighters.html |work=[[半島電視台|半島電視台]] |date=03-06-2015 |access-date=05-12-2020 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131821/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/6/3/us-coalition-has-killed-10000-isil-fighters.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

