2017年，布林肯與[[米歇爾·佛洛諾伊|米歇爾·佛洛諾伊]]、塞爾吉奧·阿奎爾（Sergio Aguirre）及尼丁·查達（Nitin Chadda）共同創立政治戰略諮詢公司「WestExec Advisors」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Michèle Flournoy|url=http://westexec.com/michele-flournoy/|publisher=WestExec Advisors|language=en|access-date=2020-05-22|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115043525/https://westexec.com/michele-flournoy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Our Team|url=http://westexec.com/our-team/|publisher=WestExec Advisors|language=en|access-date=2020-05-22|archive-date=2020-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510203137/http://westexec.com/our-team/|dead-url=no}}</ref>WestExec的客戶包括[[Google|Google]]的子公司[[Jigsaw|Jigsaw]]，以色列人工智慧公司Windward，部分名列《[[財星_(雜誌)|財星]]》雜誌100強的公司，以及無人監控機製造商Shield AI等，<ref name="gotrich">{{Cite news|first=Jonathan|last=Guyer|date=06-07-2020|title=How Biden's Foreign-Policy Team Got Rich|language=en-US|work={{link-en|美國展望|The American Prospect}}|url=https://prospect.org/world/how-biden-foreign-policy-team-got-rich/|access-date=2020-07-21|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718082955/https://prospect.org/world/how-biden-foreign-policy-team-got-rich/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Shield AI公司更與[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]簽訂了720萬美元的合約。<ref name="nyt20201128">{{Cite news|last1=Lipton|first1=Eric|last2=Vogel|first2=Kenneth P.|date=2020-11-28|title=Biden Aides' Ties to Consulting and Investment Firms Pose Ethics Test|language=en-US|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/28/us/politics/biden-westexec.html|access-date=10-12-2020|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128161047/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/28/us/politics/biden-westexec.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>據雜誌《[[外交政策_(雜誌)|外交政策]]》報道，該公司的客戶包括國防工業、私募股權公司和對沖基金。<ref name="FP">{{Cite web|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/11/23/biden-defense-pentagon-flournoy-iraq-afghanistan-yemen/|title=Biden's Likely Defense Secretary Pick Flournoy Faces Progressive Pushback|last1=Detsch|first1=Jack|last2=Gramer|first2=Robbie|work=[[外交政策_(雜誌)|外交政策]]|date=2020-11-23|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125032319/https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/11/23/biden-defense-pentagon-flournoy-iraq-afghanistan-yemen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>布林肯一共在公司中獲得近120萬美元的報酬。<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Vogel|first1=Kenneth P.|author-link1=Kenneth P. Vogel|last2=Lipton|first2=Eric|author-link2=Eric Lipton|date=02-01-2021|title=Washington Has Been Lucrative for Some on Biden's Team|language=en-US|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/01/us/politics/yellen-speaking-fees-disclosure.html|access-date=02-01-2021|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112031549/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/01/us/politics/yellen-speaking-fees-disclosure.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

