=== 外交議題 ===
2015年，布林肯指出由於土耳其是美國的重要盟友，因此評定土耳其抑或敘利亞[[庫德人|庫德人]][[人民保護部隊|人民保護部隊]]兩者誰比較好，「甚至不是值得討論的問題」。<ref>{{cite news |title=How would Blinken impact U.S.-Turkey relations as secretary of state? |url=https://ahvalnews.com/turkey-us/how-would-blinken-impact-us-turkey-relations-secretary-state |work=Ahval |date=2020-11-23 |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123110130/https://ahvalnews.com/turkey-us/how-would-blinken-impact-us-turkey-relations-secretary-state |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年，布林肯在《紐約時報》上發表評論文章，主張應為庫德人提供武器以擊敗伊斯蘭國，同時敦促美國政府應加倍支持土耳其消滅[[庫德斯坦工人黨|庫德斯坦工人黨]]。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Blinken |first1=Antony J. |title=To Defeat ISIS, Arm the Syrian Kurds |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/31/opinion/to-defeat-isis-arm-the-syrian-kurds.html |work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |access-date=2020-11-24 |date=2017-01-31 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123223916/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/31/opinion/to-defeat-isis-arm-the-syrian-kurds.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他批評時任總統特朗普決定從敘利亞北部撤軍的決定。<ref name="timesofisrael"/>2020年10月，他反對土耳其總統[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|埃爾多安]]提出的「在[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]建立兩國方案」的呼籲，稱拜登政府致力於[[賽普勒斯問題|統一塞浦路斯]]。<ref name="dw2020"/><ref>{{cite tweet|user=ABlinken|number=1321174228192952320|title=We regret calls by Turkish President Erdogan and Turkish Cypriot leader Tatar for a two-state solution in Cyprus. Joe Biden has long expressed support for a bizonal, bicommunal federation that ensures peace and prosperity for all Cypriots|date=2020-10-27}}</ref>

在[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]問題上，布林肯形容事件為「徹底混亂」。<ref name="sharpbreak">{{Cite news|last=Borger|first=Julian|author-link=Julian Borger|date=2020-11-23|title=Antony Blinken: Biden's secretary of state nominee is sharp break with Trump era|language=en-GB|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/nov/23/antony-blinken-joe-biden-secretary-of-state-appointee-is-sharp-break-with-trump-era|access-date=2020-11-24|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124201820/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/nov/23/antony-blinken-joe-biden-secretary-of-state-appointee-is-sharp-break-with-trump-era|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布林肯在國務院任內，為重振[[北约|北约]]與修復的歐洲關係進行訪歐活動，與秘书长[[延斯·史托騰伯格|延斯·史托騰伯格]]會面，布林肯向歐洲盟友喊話「我今天来到这里，部分原因是为了与北约盟友分享我们的一些初步想法，但也许更重要的是，我是来倾听和协商，因为这是盟友需要做的。」<ref>{{cite news |title=布林肯寻求 "重振 "北约|url=https://amp.dw.com/zh/布林肯寻求-重振-北约/a-56962967?__twitter_impression=true}}</ref>，另一方面，他也來傳達美國將繼續施壓德国的態度，就德國正在推行的北溪2号项目進行威胁，此前美國已經對此進行了一輪制裁<ref>{{cite news |title=美国威胁就北溪2号项目制裁德国|url=https://m.dw.com/zh/美国威胁就北溪2号项目制裁德国/a-56960453}}</ref>。

